rts for peace and development.', 21719, 0), (436396, 'If there was a template for success in sports, everyone would follow it. You do the best you can and trust the people you trust.', 35063, 0), (436397, 'Owning a popular sports team is very different than any other type of business. They don''t throw parades when Apple has the biggest quarter in corporate history. People don''t call and email asking for anyone from the team to come visit their sick child. They don''t cry as they request a jersey of their child''s favorite player to be buried with them.', 35063, 0), (436398, 'Boxing has become America''s tragic theater.', 852, 0), (436399, 'I''m girlie in the sense that I like makeup, but I also love sports and man food.', 452, 0), (436400, 'We should reach out to people to try to go after the fans the way other sports do. Because we can''t just depend on the fact that it is a great game.', 63558, 0);
